title: Handbook - Themeforest Responsive AJAX WordPress Theme
description:
Handbook - Themeforest Responsive AJAX WordPress Theme

Weather you're a blogger, freelancer or a startup in need for the perfect blogging theme, your needs will be fulfilled as well. Write Standard posts or use other Tumblog-like format such as Status, Image, Gallery, Video, Audio, Link or Quote. Writing a Status is a really neat way of publishing small content and letting your visitors know what's going on.

To install:
1. Upload the folder to the /wp-content/themes/ directory
2. Activate the theme through the 'Themes' menu in WordPress
